# Gitignored bootstrap for headless SSH on macOS.
# Proton Pass secrets live in config.json as pass:// URIs (Homelab vault).
#
# Recommended: Proton Pass personal access token (fully headless, no macOS password on disk).
# Create on miniagent (local Terminal): pass-cli personal-access-token create --name miniagent-n8n-renovate
# Grant the token access to the Homelab vault, then paste the token here:
# PROTON_PASS_PERSONAL_ACCESS_TOKEN=pst_xxxx...xxxx::TOKENKEY
#
# Alternative: macOS login password only (unlocks keychain so pass-cli keyring session works over SSH).
# KEYCHAIN_PASSWORD_BOOTSTRAP=your-macos-login-password
